SET Description = N'Treat yourself to an unforgettable Christmas Nile Cruise adventure this year with ourEgyptat Christmas holidays. The Salacia Nile cruiseÂ is a luxurious 5-star cruise ship that will take you to the most excitingÂ historical sites along the Nile on a relaxing 5-day cruise. The comfortable Egyptian climate is the perfect way to escape cold temperatures at home this December. Your egyptologist will take you to some of the oldest and most impressive ruins of ancient Egypt, includingKarnak Temple,Luxor Temple,Valley of the Kings,Queen Hatshepsut Temple, theColossi of Memnon,Kom Ombo Temple,Horus Temple,Unfinished ObeliskandPhilae Temple. Your evenings on board will allow for plenty of rest and relaxation after each day of exploration, with exciting and varied local entertainment each night.
',

