Itinerary = N'● Day 1: Luxor Nile Cruise Tours: Meet & assist at Luxor Airport or railway station. Transfer to embark Nile Cruise before lunch. Embarkation before lunch. Lunch on board. Visit East Bank (Karnak Temple & Luxor Temple). Dinner on board. Overnight in Luxor. Meals: Lunch, Dinner 
● Day 2: Valley of the Kings & Edfu: Breakfast on board. Visit West Bank -- Valley of the Kings & Temple of Queen Hatshepsut. Sail to Edfu via Esna. Lunch on board. Afternoon tea. Dinner on board. Overnight in Edfu. Meals: Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner 
● Day 3: Kom Ombo Temple and Sailing to Aswan: Breakfast on board. Visit Horus Temple in Edfu. Lunch on board. Afternoon tea during Sailing to Kom Ombo. Visit the Temple shared by two gods Sobek & Haeroris in Kom Ombo. Sail to Aswan. Dinner on board. Over night in Aswan. Meals: Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner 
● Day 4: Aswan Sightseeing: Breakfast on board. Visit the Philae Temple & Unfinished Obelisk. Lunch on board. Afternoon tea. Dinner on board. Overnight in Aswan. Meals: Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner 
● Day 5: Disembarkation in Aswan: Breakfast on board. Disembarkation after breakfast. Transfer to Aswan Airport or railway station. Meals: Breakfast'
